strings.Value: "It's true, I don't need food to survive. But I hope I've made myself clear. I'll not be changing my habits for your sake."
"It's amusing to be the last sober guest at a feast. It's even better to be the only one in the party who isn't afraid of starving to death!"
"If it were up to me, you wouldn't set foot on this land. But the word of the {mf|baron|baroness|king|queen} is law."
"I realize we don't have to be friends to travel together, but can't we at least be cordial?"
"Don't worry, we don't need your charity."
"Very dignified. Only animals eat to be full. For people, food is always a ritual."
